title: BRIEF-MailUp H1 net profit falls to 7,000 euros
text:
BRIEF-MailUp H1 net profit falls to 7,000 euros Sept 28 
* Reports H1 net profit of 7,000 euros ($7,821.10) versus 64,000 euros a year ago 
* H1 production value 4.5 million euros versus 3.9 million euros a year ago 
Source text: bit.ly/1jpJIOQ Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8950 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
